

update                  System Maintenance                 update




Update file systems periodically

/etc/update

update periodically calls sync to write to the disk all file sys-
tem data that are in memory.  It never exits.

The initialization command file /etc/rc normally executes update.
It should not be executed directly.

***** See Also *****

init, sync, system maintenance











































